---
title: Cheesy Beyond Meat® and Mushroom Calzones with Marinara
description: Grab the kids and get them to help with tonight's easy cheesy Beyond Meat® calzones. The DIY garlicky sauce is the ultimate calzone dipper and comes together with just the stir of a spoon. The kids can even mix and match their fillings... it's a win-win dinner!
